#Step-by-Step Example

1. Define a Class to Serialize:
    a. Implement the Serializable interface.
    b. Add serialVersionUID for version control.
    c. Mark sensitive data as transient.

2. Serialize the Object:
    a. Use ObjectOutputStream to write the object to a file.

3. Deserialize the Object:
    a. Use ObjectInputStream to read the object from the file.